        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-num">02</div>
          <div>
            <div class="faq-q">What&rsquo;s a Physician/Doctor Loan and is it always the right product?</div>
            <div class="faq-a">Physician/Doctor Loan programs from many specialty lenders accept MDs and DOs with low-down or no-down structures (0&ndash;10% down even on jumbo amounts), no PMI requirement, IDR-friendly DTI treatment, and signed forward-looking contracts (residents qualifying on attending income up to 60-90 days pre-start). It&rsquo;s the most powerful product for many physician borrowers but not always optimal &mdash; we compare Physician Loan vs Conventional vs Jumbo pricing case-by-case based on down payment availability, loan amount, rate environment, and whether PMI removal matters at your specific equity level.</div>
